    "description": "<p>On your turn during a conflict scene, you may use an action and spend a variable amount of MP to weave voice and music into a magical effect known as a <strong>verse</strong>.</p><p>You may only sing <strong>one verse</strong> per turn, even if you have access to multiple actions.</p><p>When you first acquire this Skill, you learn <strong>all three volumes</strong>, plus <strong>one key</strong> and <strong>one tone</strong>. Whenever you acquire this Skill again, you may learn <strong>one key</strong> or <strong>one tone</strong> (your choice).</p><hr /><ul><li><p>For descriptions of how <strong>verses</strong> are broken down as well as a list of all of the Keys and Tones, please refer to the following handout: @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.handouts.JournalEntry.q4PpsRwoiMTRKUeJ]{Verses Rules}</p></li><li><p>For purposes of <strong>automation</strong>, please add the following feature to your character sheet and click on it to <strong>perform</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.nu7QnUu7tmVv6zxU]{Verse}</p></li></ul>",
